snippet.textDisplay: I love your channel and have tried many recipes with success and like them. However, this is a miss for me.  While I love cabbage eating it in a sandwich is not appealing and the ingredients are common to what most cultures use so the taste is familiar to me. However,  I prefer the Japanese Okonomiyaki of the many Asian  recipes I have tried making with cabbage. But my favorite way to eat cabbage is the good old Southern way with smoke meats/ham or pigtails a a piece of cornbread raised on a farm it just one of my favorite memory dishes made by my grandmother.  Your eye shadow is beautiful by the way. Thank you for sharing!
